		<abstract id="abstract">
			<title>Migrating Eclipse 3.x components and applications to Eclipse 4
			</title>
			<para> This tutorial gives an overview on how to migrate Eclipse
				components and application based on the Eclipse 3.x application
				model to Eclipse 4. This also includes using the
				compatibility
				layer
				in the
				Eclipse platform to run plug-ins
				based on the Eclipse
				3.x API.
			</para>
		</abstract>
